# DECISIONS

Append-only register of architectural and scope decisions. Every `/discuss`, `/plan-slice`, and `/execute-task` command reads this file and inlines it into the subagent dispatch prompt.

## Format

```
## YYYY-MM-DD — <one-line title>

**Decision.** <what was decided, one paragraph>

**Rationale.** <why — constraints, trade-offs, what was considered and rejected>

**Superseded by.** <YYYY-MM-DD link if a later decision replaces this one; leave blank otherwise>
```

